OL,3,COlder people urged to apply for
OL,4,Cpension credit as Winter Fuel
OL,5,CAllowance cut
OL,7,FAge Cymru are warning older people in
OL,8,FWales to sign up for pension credit
OL,9,Fbefore the deadline, if they want to
OL,10,Freceive a Winter fuel payment.
OL,12,FThey say more than #200 million in
OL,13,Fpension credit goes unclaimed each
OL,14,Fyear in Wales.
OL,16,FWith changes to the Winter Fuel
OL,17,FPayments, all pensioners will no
OL,18,Flonger receive money automatically,
OL,19,Finstead, only those who also receive
OL,20,Fpension credit will be eligible.
