OL,5,CAllowance cut
OL,7,FAn estimated 400,000 households in
OL,8,FWales are expected to be impacted by
OL,9,Fcuts to the Winter Fuel Allowance, the
OL,10,FUK government has confirmed.
OL,12,FMichael Phillips, from Age Cymru says
OL,13,F"there is a concern that with Winter
OL,14,Fapproaching, people may decide to keep
OL,15,Ftheir heating off, or cut back on
OL,16,Ffood, and make themselves seriously
OL,17,Fill, which would present even more
OL,18,Fproblems for our beleaguered health
OL,19,Fand social services.
