OL,7,F"We have to remember that many older
OL,8,Fpeople require more heating because
OL,9,Fthey are housebound, or have serious
OL,10,Fillnesses that require a warm home."
OL,12,FAge Cymru say in their 2024 annual
OL,13,Fsurvey of over 1300 older people
OL,14,Facross Wales, almost half of older
OL,15,Fpeople found cost of living to be a
OL,16,Fchallenge over the last 12 months, and
OL,17,Fover half of older people had issues
OL,18,Fwith their physical health.
