OL,7,FThe Chancellor has defended the move
OL,8,Fto scrap the payments for some
OL,9,Fpensioners insisting it will be offset
OL,10,Fby increases by pensions and lower
OL,11,Fenergy prices this winter compared to
OL,12,Flast year.
OL,14,FSpeaking in the House of Commons, the
OL,15,Fchancellor said she had settled on
OL,16,F"difficult decisions" - which included
OL,17,Fmaking "the winter fuel payment better
OL,18,Ftargeted" - to "put the public
OL,19,Ffinances on a sustainable footing".
